From Jon Livesey Subject Re free moral agency In article Bill Conner writes Many of the atheists posting here argue against their own parody of religion they create some ridiculous caricature of a religion and then attack the believers within that religion and the religion itself as By their own devices they establish a new religion a You mean Bobby Mozumder is a myth We wondered about The point of course is to erect an easy target and deflect the disputants away from the real issue The fictional Christian or Moslem or Jew who is supposed to believe the distorted representation of their beliefs presented here is therefore made to seem a fool and his her arguments can thereby be made to appear The mythology is the misrepresentations of religion used here as You mean Bobby Mozumder didn't really post here We wondered about that So Mr Is Bobby Mozumder a myth a performing artist a real a crackpot a provocateur You know everything and read all minds why don't you tell us